tables.table_schema:
results_table
- id INT PRIMARY KEY
- result_name TEXT
- result_value FLOAT
- timestamp TIMESTAMP

predictions_table
- id INT PRIMARY KEY
- prediction_name TEXT
- prediction_score FLOAT
- model_used TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMP

CREATE TABLE analytics (
    analytics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    result_id INT,
    prediction_id INT,
    model_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    analysis_result JSONB
);
